reviewText:
This is a Live video from the Kingsmen Quartet from 1991. Group members include Big Jim Hamill, Eldridge Fox, Greg Fox, Anthony Burger, Ray Dean Reese, Gary Sheppard, Parker Jonathan, and Gary Dillard.
Song list on this video:
I'll Be Satisfied,
We Represent the King,
A Beautiful Life,
Anthony's Salute to the Troops,
Ring Out the Welcome,
Prodigal Son,
Bought By the Blood,
Wish You Were Here,
God's In Command,
I Just Stopped By.

A very enjoyable video.
